   638|/**
   639| * Restore a snapshot back into Supabase. This OVERWRITES production data.
   640| * It requires explicit owner approval — the caller must pass `confirmed: true`
   641| * or the restore is refused.
   642| *
   643| * For each table, the restore:
   644| *   1. Reads the snapshot JSON from disk.
   645| *   2. Upserts all rows via the Supabase REST API (POST with upsert).
   646| *   3. Reports how many rows were written.
   647| *
